---
title: Chalet-Style Double Chicken Dinner with Shallot Gravy and Creamy Mash
description: Tender chicken breasts get the ultimate Canadian treatment tonight with chalet-style dry rub and savoury shallot gravy! It's only fair to serve up this main with equally cozy sides: Creamy mashed potatoes and crunchy green beans are the perfect accompaniments.
